  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nCurrently, our `LightPeerChain` implementation only has APIs for retrieving chain data from other peers, but it simply drops any requests for chain data from peers\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nIt should handle those requests for chain data. That will require our `LESPeer` implementation to grow a few APIs, some of which already exist in `tests/p2p/test_lightchain.py`\r\n",
